331
00:18:49,844 --> 00:18:53,523
<i>Nini, está tudo bem
ficar triste.</i>

332
00:18:58,576 --> 00:18:59,976
Eu sei.

333
00:19:00,755 --> 00:19:02,156
Tudo bem,
obrigada, Kourt.

334
00:19:02,434 --> 00:19:05,270
<i>Me ligue se precisar,
tudo bem?</i>

335
00:19:05,758 --> 00:19:08,363
